      "content": "thanks for the tip on the B6. i've also been having some weird blurry vision lately and my stomach feels really upset. i was reading online that these could be signs of lithium toxicity though... are you sure it's just the adjustment phase? it's making me a little nervous. should i really just stay the course or is there something else i should do right now?",
